title: Brian 'Bunger' Hurn remembered for contributions to Barossa Valley politics and Australian sport
text: Former state cricketer and baron of Barossa politics Brian 'Bunger' Hurn will be remembered for many things, but few compare to the time he ripped the heart out of the visiting England team. ...
